```python
import pandas as pd

    "time": [0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 2],
    "temp": [37.0, 37.2, 37.1, 36.8, 36.5, 36.2, 36.0, 35.8, 35.5, 37.5, 37.5, 37.5],
    "do":   [55,   53,   52,   50,   48,   45,   42,   40,   38,   60,   60,   60],
})

    "run": ["R1","R2","R3","R4"],
    "cell_line": ["CHO-A","CHO-A","CHO-B","CHO-B"],
    "temp_low": [36.5, 36.5, 35.5, 36.5],
    "temp_high": [37.5, 37.5, 36.5, 37.5],
    "do_low": [45, 45, 40, 50],
})
display(df_log, df_run)
```

```python
df_merged = df_log.merge(df_run, how='left', on='run')
display(df_merged)
df_merged_sorted = df_merged.sort_values(by=['run', 'time'])
df_feat = df_merged_sorted.groupby('run').agg(
    temp_mean = ('temp', 'mean'),
    temp_min = ('temp', 'min'),
    do_last = ('do', 'last'),
).reset_index()
display(df_feat)
df_feat = df_feat.merge(df_run[['run','cell_line','temp_low','do_low']], on='run', how='left')
df_feat['out_of_spec'] = (df_feat['temp_min'] < df_feat['temp_low']) | (df_feat['do_last'] < df_feat['do_low'])
df_feat['is_bad_run'] = (df_feat['cell_line'].eq("CHO-B")) & (df_feat['temp_mean'] < 36.2)

display(df_feat)
TP = ((df_feat['is_bad_run'])&(df_feat['out_of_spec'])).sum()
FP = ((~df_feat['is_bad_run'])&(df_feat['out_of_spec'])).sum()
TN = ((~df_feat['is_bad_run'])&(~df_feat['out_of_spec'])).sum()
FN = ((df_feat['is_bad_run'])&(~df_feat['out_of_spec'])).sum()
display(TP, FP, TN, FN)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
color = np.where(df_feat['out_of_spec'], 'red', 'gray')
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
ax.scatter(df_feat['temp_mean'], df_feat['do_last'], marker='o', color= color)
ax.set_title("Temperature vs DO (Run Summary)")
ax.set_xlabel("temp_mean")
ax.set_ylabel("do_last")
ax.grid(False)
ax.axhline(df_run['do_low'].mean(), color='gray', linestyle='--', linewidth=2)
plt.show()
```
